data.name: label1.Text
data.value: Note: if progress seems to stop, switch to iTunes and check if it is asking you a question. It might ask you to nominate a folder for the converted files. Chose any folder and click 'OK'. Or it might ask you to identify the disc from multiple entries in the Gracenote database. Click 'Cancel' in the iTunes dialog if this occurs.

data.name: labPrompt.Text
data.value: Please put Disc ## of the set into your CD drive. Wait until you see iTunes list all the tracks, then click on OK.
